replies.body:
I love Thorpe Park, England so much, favourite rides there have to be The Swarm and Stealth. I've been to Alton Towers once and liked Air a lot.
Since what has happened on the Smiler I am a little wary but I still love rollercoasters and will continue to love them.

Im really looking forward to going to Thrope Park as a kind of end of year treat with my school in a couple of days!
